Build Correlation Searches with Splunk Enterprise Security Hands On Workshop 1.0.2
24 March 2020

This app is a companion app to the Building Correlation Searches with Splunk Enterprise Security Hands-On Workshop based on the BOTS v4 data set.

It is designed to be installed on top of a Splunk ES instance and contains a module for the Use Case Library, complete with a Analytic Story containing Correlation Searches that users can apply to their own ES instance.

Many of these searches are derived from the Sigma project https://github.com/Neo23x0/sigma.

The decrypt app is required for the PowerShell Encdoding Correlation Search and can be found here: https://splunkbase.splunk.com/app/2655/.